text: Frances Jennifer Adamson, (born 20 April 1961) is an Australian politician. She is the 36th Governor of South Australia since 7 October 2021. She was the Ambassador to China from 2011 until 2016. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Ambassadors of Australia Category:Governors of South Australia Category:Politicians from Adelaide Category:Ambassadors to China
